AMEND S e n ate Bill No. 1889 House Bill No. 1708*
by deleting subdivision (k)(1)(B) in SECTION 1 and substituting instead:
(B) If the department issues a driver license or intermediate driver license
pursuant to subdivision (k)(1)(A), then the license must be non-renewable and valid for
only thirty-six (36) months.
AND FURTHER AMEND by deleting the word "restricted" in subdivision (k)(1)(C) in the
amendatory language of SECTION 1.
